text.data-name: Participants struggled to drag the carousel on the mobile design. Instead of using the prototype drag trigger, we should just use the horizontal scroll groups so that would enable users to scroll to any card they like.
text.tspan: enable users to scroll to any

text.data-name: Participants had difficulties tapping on the dropdown menu for the mobile design. Therefore, we prototyped titles and icons so that participants would not struggle to open the dropdown menu for the mobile design
